  "title": "Events Marketing (Entry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are looking for an ambitious Marketing Executive to help increase our clients’ brand awareness and customer base by promoting their products and services at event sites in Singapore.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Execute event marketing campaigns by coordinating tasks and ensuring timely completion to meet campaign goals</li><li>Promote products and services directly to existing and potential customers to increase engagement and sales</li><li>Collaborate with the Marketing team to develop and implement effective promotion strategies that drive brand visibility and customer interest</li><li>Adapt quickly to new marketing approaches and apply feedback to improve campaign outcomes</li><li>Communicate clearly and confidently with customers and team members to support marketing objectives</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Background in Sales, Marketing, or similar roles is a plus</li><li>Good communication and presentation skills are a plus</li><li>Open-minded attitude and willingness to learn new marketing skills and techniques</li></ul><p>Candidates with no prior experience are welcome to apply</p>",
